isha \n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Batman: Gotham by Gaslight]]''\n| [[Alfred Pennyworth]]\n| Voice role<br>Direct-to-video release\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Enemy at the Door]]''\n| Clive Martel\n| Episode: \"[[Enemy at the Door#Season One (1978)|Steel Hand from the Sea]]\"\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Lillie (TV series)|Lillie]]''\n| William Le Breton\n| [[ITV Network|ITV]] miniseries\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''Accident''\n| Simon Lovell\n| Episode: \"The Figures Man\"\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''{{sortname|The|Mallens}}''\n| Weir\n| Episode: 1.1 <br>Episode: 1.2\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Secret Army (TV series)|Secret Army]]''\n| Hanslick\n| Episode: \"[[List of Secret Army episodes#Series Three: 1979|A Safe Place]]\"\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Love in a Cold Climate (TV serial, 1980)|Love in a Cold Climate]]''\n| Tony Kroesig\n| [[Thames Television]] \n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Crown Court (TV series)|Crown Court]]''\n| Timothy Preston-Berry\n| Episode: \"Hen Party\"\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Bergerac (TV series)|Bergerac]]''\n| Bill\n| Episode: \"[[List of Bergerac episodes#Series 1|See You in Moscow]]\"\n|-\n| 1984\u201388\n| ''{{sortname|The|Comic Strip Presents...}}''\n| Ricki <br> Recording Studio Engineer\n| Episodes: \"[[The Comic Strip Presents...#List of Comic Strip films|Slags]]\", \"[[More Bad News]]\"\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[C.A.T.S. Eyes]]''\n| James Sinden\n| Episode: \"[[List of C.A.T.S. Eyes episodes#Series 1|Goodbye, Jenny Wren]]\"\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[Howards' Way]]''\n| Phil Norton\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''[[Boon (TV series)|Boon]]''\n| Richard Rathbone\n| Episode: \"Day of the Yoke\"\n|-\n| 1988\n| ''Pulaski''\n| Dudley Fielding\n| Episode: \"The Price of Fame\"\n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Rockliffe's Babies]]''\n| Chris Patterson\n| Episode: \"A Trip to the Zoo\"\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Woof!]]''\n| Bentley\n| Episode: 3.7 <br> Episode: 3.8\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''{{sortname|The|Detectives|The Detectives (1993 TV series)}}''\n| Simon\n| Episod